{
  "id": "adv_bond_ai_01_05",
  "title": "小美山愛5",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "おいっちにー、さんし！　はぁ、はぁ……カバンが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "One‚ two‚ three‚ four! Huff‚ puff… my bag is",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_05-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "辞書でパンパンだから、さすがに腕が疲れてきた……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so packed with dictionaries that my arms are killing me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 13.5999992371
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_05-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "（火曜は現代文と英語があるから、国語辞典と）\n（英和辞典を持って行かないといけないし……うぅ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Since Tuesday has Modern Lit and English‚ I have to carry）\n（both my Japanese and English dictionaries… ugh.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.5999992371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_05-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "（こんなことなら学校に教科書とか置いてくれば）\n（良かったかなぁ……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Maybe I should've just left my textbooks at school）\n（if I knew it would be this heavy…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 27.5333325704
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_05-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "（……いやいや、学生の本分は勉強だから置き勉なんて）\n（絶対ダメ！　ちゃんと毎日持ち歩かなきゃ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…No‚ no! A student's duty is to study‚ so leaving books）\n（behind is a big NO! I have to carry them every day.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.5333325704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_05-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "（莉央さんの学生時代は、教材以外に足に十キロの）\n（重りを付けて登校してたってこころが言ってたし）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Kokoro told me that back in Rio-san's student days‚）\n（she wore 10kg weights on her feet to school…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.3999974569,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "（私なんてまだまだだよ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（so I'm still nowhere near her level.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.8333335878,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 42.8333335878
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_05-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "（……よし、もうちょっと頑張ろう！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…Alright‚ let's push a little more!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.3333340963,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "筋トレは日々の積み重ねから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Muscle training is all about daily consistency!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.4666669211,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 48.4666669211
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_05-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "私の筋肉、気高く咲き誇れー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My muscles‚ bloom with nobility!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.5786623797,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.1333340963
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "（ふー、なんとか到着したけど……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Phew‚ I finally made it‚ but…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.1333307904,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_05-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "（沢山歩いたせいか凄くお腹空いてきたな……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I'm so hungry after all that walking…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.7666674297,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hungry-01.m4a",
          "delay": 899.9999999999986
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.5333307904
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_05-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "（……授業始まる前なら、ちょっとくらい）\n（お弁当食べても大丈夫だよね？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…If it's before class starts‚ maybe it's okay）\n（to eat a little bit of my lunch?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.5333307904,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_05-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "（みんなに見つからないように、教科書を立てて……）\n（よし、完璧！　いただきまーす！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I'll set up my textbooks so nobody can see…）\n（Alright‚ perfect! Time to eat!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.1666641237,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2533.338419499998
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2533.338419499998
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.500000763
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "う……！　は、箸が重いっ……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh…! The‚ the chopsticks are so heavy…!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.2666641237,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_05-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "なんで……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why…!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.8333340963,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "（そ、そうだ……！　こころに莉央さんは学生時代）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Oh‚ that's right…! Kokoro told me that Rio-san used）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.4666641237,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.4666641237
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_05-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "（毎日すっごく重い箸を使ってたって言われて……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（super heavy chopsticks every day when she was a student…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.0333340963,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_05-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "（慌ててお父さんの知り合いに特注で作ってもらった）\n（『ダンベル箸』にしたの忘れてた～！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（and I forgot I switched to the 'Dumbbell Chopsticks'）\n（I had custom-made by my dad's acquaintance!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.6666620892,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "（朝、なんだかいつもより荷物が重いと）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I did think my bag felt heavier than usual）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.2999954225,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.2999954225
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_05-ai014.m4a",
      "text": "（思ったんだよね～……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（this morning~…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.5042006894,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "（うう、箸が重くてうまく鶏ささみ焼きが掴めない……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Ugh‚ the chopsticks are so heavy I can't pick up the grilled chicken…）",
        "id": ""
