      "startTime": 108.0333287558,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.0333287558
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_05-ai015.m4a",
      "text": "（だんだん指がしびれてきた……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（My fingers are starting to go numb…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.4333340963,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_05-ai016.m4a",
      "text": "（……でも、莉央さんはもっと過酷な訓練を）\n（日々こなしてきたんだよね）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…But Rio-san overcame even harsher training）\n（every single day.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.1333318076,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "（なら、私がここで音を上げる訳にはいかないよ！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（So I can't give up here!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.5666600547,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.5666600547
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_05-ai017.m4a",
      "text": "（根性だけは、負けないんだから……！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I won't lose when it comes to sheer guts…!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.2999972027,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
